Notes: Wheaton's Harris hits game-winner with one second remaining, snapping SP's
12-game win streak, its second-longest in school history...Wheaton jumped out
to 15-4 lead over first 12 minutes...SP took first lead at 33-31 with 8:41
left and led 38-33, but did not score a field goal in final five minutes.
Game.Officials: Tom Thornton,  John Dacey,  Doug Mullaney
